name: Oxford Art Online - Benezit Dictionary of Artists
description: With nearly 170,000 entries on artists from antiquity to the present day and featuring regular updates, Benezit contains thousands of auction records, museum holdings, and bibliographies. In addition to its outstanding scope and depth, two features in particular make Benezit unique among art reference works: its superb coverage of obscure artists and the inclusion of images of artistsÛª signatures, monograms, and stamps.
